49:01.680 --> 49:03.520
And I think that as a result, when

49:03.520 --> 49:07.400
we look at non-humans when they vocalize or gesture

49:07.400 --> 49:08.840
or any other way, we assume that there

49:08.840 --> 49:11.880
must be something similar going on.

