49:21.800 --> 49:24.720
Because this is one of my favorite subjects right now.

49:24.720 --> 49:27.760
Because, again, you go back to ancient times.

49:27.760 --> 49:29.880
And the idea was that language and speech

49:29.880 --> 49:31.720
was inextricably linked.

49:31.720 --> 49:34.360
Ratio and ratio is what they talked about.

